outputs.output_descr: Support Ministry of Social Development and Human Security and relevant agencies to map out and review existing databases on gender-based violence and set up a local-level gender-based violence database at the local level in the pilot areas.

project_descr: Every Home a Safe Home: Supporting Thailand Towards Effective Implementation of Protection of Domestic Violence Victims Act BE 2550 (2007)
project_title: Supporting implementation of Domestic Violence Act 2007
